reviewText: Easy to use a mobile. If you're taller than 4ft, be ready to tuck your legs behind you as you hang and pull.

reviewText: Love this feeder. Heavy duty & capacity. Best feature is the large varmint guard. Definitely use a small lock or securing device on the battery housing latch. I gave 4 stars because several bolts were missing. Check contents b4 beginning.
summary: Great feeder. Would recommend for use for those that can't check a feeder regularly. Solid varmint guard.
